**APIFluxProbe**  
**Description:**  
Monitors a dynamic set of APIs for flux in latency, status code changes, and behavior drift over time.

```markdown
# APIFluxProbe - Adaptive API Monitor

APIFluxProbe captures and visualizes fluctuations in API performance across multiple endpoints and timeframes.

## Features
- Drift and anomaly alerting  
- Latency curve tracking  
- CSV / JSON export

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/APIFluxProbe.git
cd APIFluxProbe
python monitor.py
